txt.en: Within Agal Dûn, the fortress of horror, Angmarim of the Iron Crown watch over Câr Bronach. Behind its wall, Angmarim gather supplies and altars for their vile rituals. In steps to reclaim Câr Bronach, these supplies and altars must be destroyed.
Within Agal Dûn, the fortress of horror, Angmarim of the Iron Crown watch over Câr Bronach.
Agal Dûn can be found in central Câr Bronach.\n\nYou should destroy altars and supplies at Agal Dûn.
